    <string name="about_description">
        <![CDATA[
<p> <b> Money Planner </b> allows you to specify the amount of money you will have at any time. </p>
        <p> Just specify your constant <b> Incomes </b> (salary, quarterly bonus, rental income from property, etc.)
        and <b> Expenses </b> (rent, mortgage, school fees, etc.). Also you need to  specify the means you already have (bank account, cash, etc.) in the <b> Accounts </b> . </p>
        <p> To obtain more accurate results, as well as monitoring of your finances, add <b> single </b> incomes and expenses after each transaction with the money. </p>
        <p> It is very important for the correct calculation of the final amount to  indicate actual values in the <b> Accounts </b> before starting of the calculation ! </p>
        <p> All data that you enter are stored only on your phone and are not transferred to third parties! </p>
<p>Thank you for downloading of this application! We hope that it will be useful to you. </p>
        <p align = "right"> <b> Money Planner 1.0 </b> </p>
        ]]>
